name: HK
bio:
HK is a Bay Area native DJ and upcoming producer who is truly about the music. She believes that music is the most healing and wonderful avenue to bring people together. From tech house to melodic techno HK has an eclectic taste that she curates into sets of many genres; hoping that some of her favorite track choices will land on the ears of someone who can experience something new and unique.Â 

She loves sharing her passion for music with people by playing tracks that not only will make them move, but make them feel different. To her, music isn't just an art, it's also a language and medium to establish a connection to your soul. She hopes that every set takes you on a musical journey where you can be free, lost and then find yourself again.
